Commonwealth of PA-DEPARTMENT OF ENVIRONMENTAL RESOURCES,
v.
WORKERS' COMPENSATION APPEAL BOARD (VICINELLY) Petition of: Raoul A. Vicinelly No. 324 WAL 2018 Supreme Court of Pennsylvania. May 29, 2019

ORDER

PER CURIAM .

AND NOW, this 29th day of May, 2019, the Petition for Allowance of Appeal is DENIED.

Justice Wecht did not participate in the consideration or decision of this matter.
